            "subheading": "Shot Tracking",
            "heading": "Automatically Capture Your Shots",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Seamlessly track and record your shots on the course. Now with new shot tracking technology, the best shot tracking got better.</p>",
            "button_label": "Learn More",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/automatic-shot-tracking",
