            "subheading": "Smart Distances",
            "heading": "Know Your <em>True</em> Yardages",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Know exactly how far you hit all your clubs, now calculated considering the conditions at the moment you hit the shot, to effectively \"normalize\" them so you select the right club every time.</p>",
